alright as most fo you know Ive been going back and forth from operating systems for a while. Only sticking with windows because it supporst World of warcraft compared to linux which doesnt. So im not to thrilled about windows at all. Well the more I read about vista, Microsofts next Operating system, the more excited I get about it. Im all about performance, I upgrade everything in my computer as fast as I can because I love to push the limit of computers. Well there are two features vista has that xp doesnt and can certainly use. Its called "Superfetch" and the use of external memory devices. What windows xp does now is when you load an application like photoshop or warcraft that program is loaded into you ram(memory). When you exit the application a little piece of that program stays in memory in case you need to start that program again during THAT session. Shutdown erases that little piece so it takes a long time to start again. Well Vista kinda learns what you use most. So with me running warcraft everyday it will always be in memory making it load extremely fast. Also, some of you now know that adding ram to your computer speeds it up. well what if you can add that ram in the form of a usb drive??? Enter vistas "external memory device" support. Lets says you have a 512mb usb drive laying around and never use. Dont throw it out, add that to your comps ram. So if you only have 256mb of ram, your now up to 768MB. Thats a nice improvement. So instead of having windows use whats called the pagefile system(programs running off of the the hdd instead of the ram or both) will now have more space to run off ram which is much quicker also meaning faster load times. I can go on and on about the improvements im reading but im exhausted so im going to sleep. L8r all.

Abraham Lincoln was elected to Congress in 1846.
John F. Kennedy was elected to Congress in 1946.

Abraham Lincoln was elected President in 1860.
John F. Kennedy was elected President in 1960.

Both were particularly concerned with civil rights.
Both wives lost their children while living in the White House.

Both Presidents were shot on a Friday.
Both Presidents were shot in the head.

Now it gets really weird.

Lincoln 's secretary was named Kennedy.
Kennedy's Secretary was named Lincoln.

Both were assassinated by Southerners.
Both were succeeded by Southerners named Johnson.

Andrew Johnson, who succeeded Lincoln, was born in 1808.
Lyndon Johnson, who succeeded Kennedy, was born in 1908.

John Wilkes Booth, who assassinated Lincoln, was born in 1839.
Lee Harvey Oswald, who assassinated Kennedy, was born in 1939.

Both assassins were known by their three names.
Both names are composed of fifteen letters.

Now hang on to your seat.

Lincoln was shot at the theater named 'Ford.'
Kennedy was shot in a car called ' Lincoln' made by 'Ford.'

Lincoln w as shot in a theater and his assassin ran and hid in a warehouse.
Kennedy was shot from a warehouse and his assassin ran and hid in a theater.

Booth and Oswald were assassinated before their trials.

And here's the kicker...

A week before Lincoln was shot, he was in Monroe, Maryland
A week before Kennedy was shot, he was with Marilyn Monroe.

well tonite was wierd. I hung out with grover the whole day. we're bored so we're chillin in my pool and david says "lets go to sawgrass park." I say why to look for aliens??? and he says yea. SO i say ok. my brother and his friend travis want to come too. So we hang around my house till about 11pm then we walk down 62nd ave to the st.pete times building and and walk the creek all the way back to where the water towers are and I see a gaurd outside so we turn back. Travis says that instead of walking all the way back around we could go through the sewer right back into my neighbor hood since we're right next to it. Looks safe so we all head down into the sewer. lol this is no short sewer or big either. we are all walking like we are catchers on a baseball team for about 100ft. We get to the part where the gutter goes into the road and my brother and travis(who are smaller then me and dave) wiggle out of the sewer onto the street. This is right in front of travis's house, well his aunt comes out right at the same time so him and my brother take off running as not to be seen. Me and david are stuck down there cause we cant fit to wiggle out so we have to turn around and basically crawl all the way back. It was very uncomfortable. I didnt think david was going to make it though. I get out first and I noticed flashlights right across the creek. So I turn mine on and ask them if they have seen a dog lol. They say no and ask  if im ok, im like yea, im just looking for a black german shephard and they say "well let you know if we see it." Like they know who I am. lol Well david finally gets out of the sewer and we walk back to my house to meet up with travis and my brother. At this point me and david are soaked with nasty sewer water GROSS and sweat. So we change. and then we go back to another part of my neighborhood and find a way into the locked park through someones yard. Well after you walk through the yard you come to this open field all lit up by lights from the water towers. So we run across and come to the creek again past the security post and climb under the fence thats there. When we finally get into the park close to the gate we all see something different. My brother sees blue eyes travis sees a wierd fog take form, david sees a fence and then I see "somethign crawl or walk right out in front of the fence and stop. its kneeled over and something smaller is walking towards then away from it. Well Ive seen wierd shit back there before so I start to back off but everyone wants to go closer. SO I walk out in front of them and watch this wierd bent over thing. Then there is a little blue flash of light. the size of a firefly but not a firefly, because they arent blue, they dont explode and it doesnt move over 20 feet in one second about 30 feet away from you. after the first flash david says"what the fuck was that" really loud. As soon as he said that, that wierd thing I was watching looks at us and then there was a second flash a lot closer maybe 10 ft from us. Lol I take off running the oppisite direction and I hear david travis and my borther following me. well we walk all the way back home and its about 130am when we finally go over whats happened. As we are talking about it all the power in my house goes out with a sudden flash. We are all stunned. I wait a minute and go and reset the fuse for the house. What a wierd and very long night. Im gonna take a shower now and them im going to sleep. Hope im here in the morning lol l8r all
